Description: Digital photograph (colour); view of engraved rock art on top of stone block on ground, showing dynastic Egyptian figure of man, upright and facing right, wearing skirt and adornments, holding spear or staff in right hand, incised in outline. Head is rubbed away and part cut off edge of block. Photographer’s feet visible at side of image. 10cm photo scale fitted at base of image. New Kalabsha, Egypt. Scanned
Acquisition name: Donated by: Trust for African Rock Art
